-## 1. Project purpose
-
-`upp_render` will provide a modern rendering architecture for Ultimate++ while preserving the existing U++ control, layout, input, event and theming systems.
-
-The intended pipeline is:
+## Pipeline
 
 ```text
-Ctrl::Paint
-    Γåô
-UiPaintContext
+Drawing caller
     Γåô
 UiCanvas
     Γåô
-UiDisplayList
-    Γåô
-UiRenderer2D
